title: FIVE Painting Mistakes That I Try Not to Make
description:
Here are FIVE mistakes I try not to make in my miniature painting - I hope these can help.

Vince Venturella and I made a game! Check out Reign in Hell - Demonic Skirmish Combat at http://www.reigninhellgame.com
